      "message": "If we\u0027re going to replace the API, let\u0027s please put in the work to define a new struct that is not marked `__attribute__((packed))`:\n\nhttps://github.com/openbmc/libpldm/blob/df0a2219c0f3a3f6aeeed2b9f3dabbe37911e36e/CONTRIBUTING.md#L181",
