        "id": 1000009
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-07T01:18:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "... this now combines two different return value semantics.\n\nAll new APIs must return a negative errno value on error:\n\nhttps://github.com/openbmc/libpldm/blob/df0a2219c0f3a3f6aeeed2b9f3dabbe37911e36e/CONTRIBUTING.md#L254",
      "revId": "2b472ea27be9b3fa5d6aea93711b424b1f0863da",
